Package viewAccessories

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ShrinkIcon
    An Icon that when necessary reduces the size of its image to fit within the component area, excluding any border or insets, optionally maintaining the image's aspect ratio by padding and centering the scaled image horizontally or vertically.
    StretchIcon
    An Icon that scales its image to fill the component area, excluding any border or insets, optionally maintaining the image's aspect ratio by padding and centering the scaled image horizontally or vertically.
    ThumbnailIcon
    An Icon that maintains a defined size independent of the size of the image it contains.
